function Start()
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	idDeserter = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(S_DES_FOLLOWER)	
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idDeserter) then
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idDeserter, LOC_DES_MID_FACING)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_WASPS, id_Self, idDeserter)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, snoQuest)
	--when bugs die, send deserter follower to static's position
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	idDeserter = Hydra.QuestGetFollower(S_DES_FOLLOWER)	
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idDeserter) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idDeserter)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idDeserter, false)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idDeserter, ID_DES_MID, "NPC_RUN", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idDeserter, ID_DES_MID)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idDeserter, animSetPeaceful, false, true)
		Hydra.QActorWait(idDeserter, 1.0)
		Hydra.QActorDelete(idDeserter)
	end
	
end

function Start()
	--Declarations
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	cloneDeserter = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_DES_START)
	cloneRef2 = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_REF_02_START)
	cloneRef3 = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_REF_03_START)
	
	--set anim set on wounded mid guy so we can remove it later
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_REF_01_MID, "NPC_Idle_Stand_Talk_Injured")
	
	--spawn enemies
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(ID_DES_START, "SPAWN")
	
	--If clones exist, move them
	--refugee validation is only checked if deserter is valid
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(cloneDeserter) then
		--deserter movement
		Hydra.ActorSetUseAlternateName(cloneDeserter, true)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_WAIT, id_Self, cloneDeserter)
		Hydra.QActorWait(cloneDeserter, 0.2)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(cloneDeserter, ID_DES_MID, "NPC_RUN_SLOW", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(cloneDeserter)		

		--cloneRef2 validation and movement
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(cloneRef2) then	
			Hydra.QActorWait(cloneRef2, 1)
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(cloneRef2, ID_REF_02_MID, "NPC_RUN_SLOW", true)
			Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(cloneRef2, ID_REF_02_MID)
			Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(cloneRef2)
		end
	
		--cloneRef3 valiodation and movement
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(cloneRef3) then	
			Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(cloneRef3)
			Hydra.QActorWait(cloneRef3, 0.2)
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(cloneRef3, ID_REF_03_MID, "NPC_RUN_SLOW", true)
			Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(cloneRef3, ID_REF_03_MID)
			Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(cloneRef3)
		end		
		
	end
end
